'''Remi Eriksen''' is the current Group President and [[Chief Executive Officer]] of [[DNV GL]], an international [[classification society]] and [[certification body]]. He assumed the position since August 1, 2015, succeeding former CEO [[Henrik O. Madsen]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maritime-executive.com/article/remi-eriksen-proud-and-confident|title=Remi Eriksen: Proud and Confident|work=The Maritime Executive|accessdate=19 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/person.asp?personId=11326341&privcapId=22534286|title=Remi Eriksen: Executive Profile & Biography - Businessweek|work=Businessweek.com|accessdate=19 October 2015}}</ref><ref>http://www.tu.no/industri/2015/05/28/dnv-gl-sjef-madsen-gar-av-remi-erikasen-tar-trolig-over</ref>

